      "content": "hey im in rio right now and its so hot today. i was out walking and now im feeling really weird. my head feels heavy and i cant really find the right words when i try to talk... like they are on the tip of my tongue but i cant say them. i think i might just be super dehydrated or having heat exhaustion? what should i do to feel better?",
